welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Sweden, the land of breathtaking landscapes, rich culture, and friendly locals. We hope you have a wonderful time exploring our charming cities and experiencing our famous hospitality. Enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories!"

terminals.description: The main terminal at Greater Rochester International Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'ROC Free WiFi' from their device's available networks.
